<p>The numerical list pattern is used to show a list of ranked links in the aside of a WordPress blog site.</p>

<h3>Rules for numerical lists</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Must only be used within an aside.</li>
    <li>Must only be used on blog sites.</li>
    <li>Must only have one list per page.</li>
    <li>There must be no more than ten links.</li>
    <li>There must be no fewer than five links.</li>
</ul>

